A devastating conflict has been foreseen, and the world\'s end is imminent. In order to heal it, the Master of Masters gives his disciples unique roles and instructs them to form Unions comprised of other Keyblade wielders. Soon afterwards, the Master vanishes.\n\n(Source: KH Wikia)'
